To generate a GitHub OAuth token for the GFM (GitHub Flavored Markdown) IDEA Plugin, follow these steps:

1. Go to GitHub > Personal Settings > Personal Access Tokens : https://github.com/settings/tokens

2. Check Generate new token

3. Select the 'public_repo' scope

4. Go to IntelliJ IDEA > Preferences > Other settings > Gfm settings, and enter the token.
